Investment inflows boost Philippine peso at close . - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - Sept 10 - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - * Banks await next Central Bank move on rates - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - The Philippine peso recovered some ground on Tuesday , drawing strength from dollar inflows for portfolio investments , traders said . The peso closed at 26 . 228 to the dollar versus 26 . 235 on Monday . The day ' s average was 26 . 229 pesos from 26 . 232 . Volume was lower at $ 105 million compared with $ 114 . 50 million . 
